h ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has angels who journey through the earth to convey to me the greetings of peace from my nation.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 1282 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21780,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/01\/29\/peace-prophet-ten-fold\/","url_meta":{"origin":40501,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: Send peace upon the Prophet, receive it ten fold","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 29, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Talha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came to us one day with a cheerful face. We said, \u201cWe see you smiling.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, the angel came to me, and he said: O Muhammad, your Lord has asked if would you not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8167,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/prophet-encourages-huriyyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":40501,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Freedom: The Prophet encourages freeing slaves, prisoners","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"e